{
  "stem": "979.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And what they would do-- and they needed 40 people to do the job for them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Nazis weren't gonna do it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So this time they chose 40 Greek, young Jewish men to-- for-- and they-- what they did with them, they worked there for three months.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they threw them in the gas chambers, because they didn't know-- they didn't want the world to know what they did.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that day, the Greeks, they were so annoyed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took two Nazis and threw the two Nazis in the gas chamber-- the ones who were telling them to do this.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then the chaos, the noise, the screaming everywhere, everywhere-- what are they doing?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they said, the-- some-- then we found out that somebody killed two Nazis, and now they are all punished, or whatever they were going to do to them.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know what happened after that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then all I know-- that a couple a weeks later, a week later, the men were leaving.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were going-- many men from the-- from the-- from the men's camp, they had them on lines.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They won't know where they were taking them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's one of them was my brother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we never knew where he went.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They told us that if they-- if they put you in trains, don't get in, because they are bringing you to another camp where there is gas chambers so that you don't get upset.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I say, even if we went-- I say, they can-- they can stop us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They can put us in a gas chamber even if we don't want to.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the thing is, they took them in another-- took them to Germany.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think they took them away, because of this that had happened.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
